[{"file": "../28/MECW28-001.html", "title": "Das Kapital", "headings": [{"tag": "title", "text": "Capital", "level": 0, "id": null, "source_file": "../28/MECW28-001.html", "chapter_number": 1, "filename": "../28/MECW28-001.html"}]}, {"file": "MECW29-002.html", "title": "Preface to Marx-Engels Collected Works Volume (29)", "headings": [{"tag": "h1", "text": "Preface to Marx-Engels Collected Works Volume (29)", "level": 0, "id": null, "source_file": "MECW29-002.html", "chapter_number": 2, "filename": "MECW29-002.html"}]}, {"file": "../28/MECW28-003.html", "title": "Foundations of the Critique of Political Economy (Grundrisse)", "headings": [{"tag": "title", "text": "Grundrisse", "level": 0, "id": null, "source_file": "../28/MECW28-003.html", "chapter_number": 3, "filename": "../28/MECW28-003.html"}]}, {"file": "MECW29-004.html", "title": "Foundations of the Critique of Political Economy (Grundrisse)", "headings": [{"tag": "h1", "text": "Foundations of the Critique of Political Economy (Grundrisse)", "level": 0, "id": null, "source_file": "MECW29-004.html", "chapter_number": 4, "filename": "MECW29-004.html"}, {"tag": "h4", "text": "Note from MIA", "level": 4, "id": "ME29-4-2", "source_file": "MECW29-004.html", "chapter_number": 4, "filename": "MECW29-004.html"}]}, {"file": "../28/MECW28-008.html#ME28-8-20", "title": "III. Chapter on Capital - Section 2: Circulation process of Capital", "headings": [{"tag": "title", "text": "[III. Chapter on Capital]", "level": 0, "id": null, "source_file": "../28/MECW28-008.html#ME28-8-20", "chapter_number": 5, "filename": "../28/MECW28-008.html#ME28-8-20"}]}, {"file": "MECW29-006.html", "title": "III. Chapter on Capital - Section 3: Capital as Fructiferous. Transformation of Surplus Value into Profit", "headings": [{"tag": "h1", "text": "III. Chapter on Capital - Section 3: Capital as Fructiferous. Transformation of Surplus Value into Profit", "level": 0, "id": null, "source_file": "MECW29-006.html", "chapter_number": 6, "filename": "MECW29-006.html"}, {"tag": "h5", "text": "Rate of profit. – Fall of the rate of profit. – Rate of profit. – Sum of profit. – Atkinson. A. Smith. Ramsay. Ricardo. – Surplus value as  profit  always expresses a lesser proportion. – Wakefield. Carey. Bastiat", "level": 5, "id": "ME29-6-2", "source_file": "MECW29-006.html", "chapter_number": 6, "filename": "MECW29-006.html"}, {"tag": "h5", "text": "Capital and revenue (profit). Production and distribution. Sismondi. – Production costs from capital's viewpoint. Profit, ditto. – Inequality of profits. Equalization and communal rate of profit. – Transformation of surplus value into profit. – Laws", "level": 5, "id": "ME29-6-3", "source_file": "MECW29-006.html", "chapter_number": 6, "filename": "MECW29-006.html"}, {"tag": "h5", "text": "Surplus value =  relation of surplus labour to necessary labour", "level": 5, "id": "ME29-6-4", "source_file": "MECW29-006.html", "chapter_number": 6, "filename": "MECW29-006.html"}, {"tag": "h5", "text": "Value of fixed capital  and its  productive power.  Durability of fixed capital, ditto. – The powers of society, division of labour etc.  cost  capital nothing. – Distinction between this and machinery (capitalist's  economy  in the employment of machinery). – Profit and surplus value", "level": 5, "id": "ME29-6-5", "source_file": "MECW29-006.html", "chapter_number": 6, "filename": "MECW29-006.html"}, {"tag": "h5", "text": "Machinery and surplus labour. Recapitulation of the doctrine of surplus value generally", "level": 5, "id": "ME29-6-6", "source_file": "MECW29-006.html", "chapter_number": 6, "filename": "MECW29-006.html"}, {"tag": "h5", "text": "Relation between the objective conditions of production. Change in the proportion of the component parts of capital", "level": 5, "id": "ME29-6-7", "source_file": "MECW29-006.html", "chapter_number": 6, "filename": "MECW29-006.html"}, {"tag": "h5", "text": "Money and fixed capital:  presupposes certain amount of wealth.  (Economist.) –  Relation of fixed capital and circulating capital. Cotton-spinner  (Economist)", "level": 5, "id": "ME29-6-8", "source_file": "MECW29-006.html", "chapter_number": 6, "filename": "MECW29-006.html"}, {"tag": "h5", "text": "Slavery and wage labour (Steuart). – Profit upon alienation.  Steuart", "level": 5, "id": "ME29-6-9", "source_file": "MECW29-006.html", "chapter_number": 6, "filename": "MECW29-006.html"}, {"tag": "h5", "text": "Wool industry in England since Elizabeth  (Tuckett). –  Silk-manufacture (Same). Ditto Iron. Cotton", "level": 5, "id": "ME29-6-10", "source_file": "MECW29-006.html", "chapter_number": 6, "filename": "MECW29-006.html"}, {"tag": "h5", "text": "Origin of free wage labour.  Vagabondage.  Tuckett", "level": 5, "id": "ME29-6-11", "source_file": "MECW29-006.html", "chapter_number": 6, "filename": "MECW29-006.html"}, {"tag": "h5", "text": "Blake  on accumulation and rate of profit. (Shows that prices etc. not indifferent because a class of mere consumers does not at the same time consume and reproduce.) – Dormant capital", "level": 5, "id": "ME29-6-12", "source_file": "MECW29-006.html", "chapter_number": 6, "filename": "MECW29-006.html"}, {"tag": "h5", "text": "Domestic agriculture at the beginning of the sixteenth century.  Tuckett", "level": 5, "id": "ME29-6-13", "source_file": "MECW29-006.html", "chapter_number": 6, "filename": "MECW29-006.html"}, {"tag": "h5", "text": "Profit. Interest. Influence of machinery on the wage fund.  Westminster Review", "level": 5, "id": "ME29-6-14", "source_file": "MECW29-006.html", "chapter_number": 6, "filename": "MECW29-006.html"}, {"tag": "h5", "text": "[  Money as measure of values and yardstick of prices. Critique of theories of the standard measure of money.  ]", "level": 5, "id": "ME29-6-15", "source_file": "MECW29-006.html", "chapter_number": 6, "filename": "MECW29-006.html"}, {"tag": "h5", "text": "[More on the critique of theories about medium of circulation and money. –  Transformation of the medium of circulation into money. – Formation of treasures. – Means of payment. – Prices of commodities and quantity of circulating money. – Value of money  ]", "level": 5, "id": "ME29-6-16", "source_file": "MECW29-006.html", "chapter_number": 6, "filename": "MECW29-006.html"}, {"tag": "h5", "text": "Capital, not labour,  determines the value of the commodity. Torrens", "level": 5, "id": "ME29-6-17", "source_file": "MECW29-006.html", "chapter_number": 6, "filename": "MECW29-006.html"}, {"tag": "h5", "text": "The minimum of wages", "level": 5, "id": "ME29-6-18", "source_file": "MECW29-006.html", "chapter_number": 6, "filename": "MECW29-006.html"}, {"tag": "h5", "text": "1826 cotton machinery and workmen.  Hodgskin", "level": 5, "id": "ME29-6-19", "source_file": "MECW29-006.html", "chapter_number": 6, "filename": "MECW29-006.html"}, {"tag": "h5", "text": "How the machine creates raw material. Linen industry. Tow yarn.  Economist", "level": 5, "id": "ME29-6-20", "source_file": "MECW29-006.html", "chapter_number": 6, "filename": "MECW29-006.html"}, {"tag": "h5", "text": "Machinery and surplus labour", "level": 5, "id": "ME29-6-21", "source_file": "MECW29-006.html", "chapter_number": 6, "filename": "MECW29-006.html"}]}, {"file": "../28/MECW28-004.html", "title": "Addenda to the Chapters on Money and on Capital", "headings": [{"tag": "title", "text": "[Addenda to the Chapters on Money and on Capital]", "level": 0, "id": null, "source_file": "../28/MECW28-004.html", "chapter_number": 7, "filename": "../28/MECW28-004.html"}]}, {"file": "MECW29-008.html", "title": "A Contribution to the Critique of Political Economy", "headings": [{"tag": "h1", "text": "A Contribution to the Critique of Political Economy", "level": 0, "id": null, "source_file": "MECW29-008.html", "chapter_number": 8, "filename": "MECW29-008.html"}, {"tag": "h3", "text": "Introductory note from Marx-Engels Collected Works, Volume 29", "level": 3, "id": "ME29-8-2", "source_file": "MECW29-008.html", "chapter_number": 8, "filename": "MECW29-008.html"}]}, {"file": "MECW29-009.html", "title": "Preface", "headings": [{"tag": "h1", "text": "Preface", "level": 0, "id": null, "source_file": "MECW29-009.html", "chapter_number": 9, "filename": "MECW29-009.html"}]}, {"file": "MECW29-010.html", "title": "Chapter 1: The Commodity", "headings": [{"tag": "h1", "text": "Chapter 1: The Commodity", "level": 0, "id": null, "source_file": "MECW29-010.html", "chapter_number": 10, "filename": "MECW29-010.html"}]}, {"file": "MECW29-011.html", "title": "Note A. Historical Notes on the Analysis of Commodities", "headings": [{"tag": "h1", "text": "Note A. Historical Notes on the Analysis of Commodities", "level": 0, "id": null, "source_file": "MECW29-011.html", "chapter_number": 11, "filename": "MECW29-011.html"}]}, {"file": "MECW29-012.html", "title": "Chapter 2: Money or Simple Circulation", "headings": [{"tag": "h1", "text": "Chapter 2: Money or Simple Circulation", "level": 0, "id": null, "source_file": "MECW29-012.html", "chapter_number": 12, "filename": "MECW29-012.html"}, {"tag": "h2", "text": "1. Measure of Value", "level": 2, "id": "ME29-12-2", "source_file": "MECW29-012.html", "chapter_number": 12, "filename": "MECW29-012.html"}, {"tag": "h2", "text": "2. Medium of Exchange", "level": 2, "id": "ME29-12-3", "source_file": "MECW29-012.html", "chapter_number": 12, "filename": "MECW29-012.html"}, {"tag": "h3", "text": "a. The Metamorphosis of Commodities", "level": 3, "id": "ME29-12-4", "source_file": "MECW29-012.html", "chapter_number": 12, "filename": "MECW29-012.html"}, {"tag": "h3", "text": "b. The Circulation of Money", "level": 3, "id": "ME29-12-5", "source_file": "MECW29-012.html", "chapter_number": 12, "filename": "MECW29-012.html"}, {"tag": "h3", "text": "c. Coins and Tokens of Value", "level": 3, "id": "ME29-12-6", "source_file": "MECW29-012.html", "chapter_number": 12, "filename": "MECW29-012.html"}, {"tag": "h2", "text": "3. Money", "level": 2, "id": "ME29-12-7", "source_file": "MECW29-012.html", "chapter_number": 12, "filename": "MECW29-012.html"}, {"tag": "h3", "text": "a. Hoarding", "level": 3, "id": "ME29-12-8", "source_file": "MECW29-012.html", "chapter_number": 12, "filename": "MECW29-012.html"}, {"tag": "h3", "text": "b. Means of Payment", "level": 3, "id": "ME29-12-9", "source_file": "MECW29-012.html", "chapter_number": 12, "filename": "MECW29-012.html"}, {"tag": "h3", "text": "c. World Money", "level": 3, "id": "ME29-12-10", "source_file": "MECW29-012.html", "chapter_number": 12, "filename": "MECW29-012.html"}, {"tag": "h2", "text": "4. The precious metals", "level": 2, "id": "ME29-12-11", "source_file": "MECW29-012.html", "chapter_number": 12, "filename": "MECW29-012.html"}]}, {"file": "MECW29-013.html", "title": "Note B. Theories of the Standard of Money", "headings": [{"tag": "h1", "text": "Note B. Theories of the Standard of Money", "level": 0, "id": null, "source_file": "MECW29-013.html", "chapter_number": 13, "filename": "MECW29-013.html"}]}, {"file": "MECW29-014.html", "title": "Note C. Theories of the the Medium of Circulation and of Money", "headings": [{"tag": "h1", "text": "Note C. Theories of the the Medium of Circulation and of Money", "level": 0, "id": null, "source_file": "MECW29-014.html", "chapter_number": 14, "filename": "MECW29-014.html"}]}, {"file": "MECW29-015.html", "title": "Appendix: Introduction by Karl Marx", "headings": [{"tag": "h1", "text": "Appendix: Introduction by Karl Marx", "level": 0, "id": null, "source_file": "MECW29-015.html", "chapter_number": 15, "filename": "MECW29-015.html"}, {"tag": "h2", "text": "I. Production, Consumption, Distribution, Exchange (Circulation)", "level": 2, "id": "ME29-15-2", "source_file": "MECW29-015.html", "chapter_number": 15, "filename": "MECW29-015.html"}, {"tag": "h3", "text": "1. Production", "level": 3, "id": "ME29-15-3", "source_file": "MECW29-015.html", "chapter_number": 15, "filename": "MECW29-015.html"}, {"tag": "h3", "text": "2. The general relations of production, of distribution, exchange and consumption", "level": 3, "id": "ME29-15-4", "source_file": "MECW29-015.html", "chapter_number": 15, "filename": "MECW29-015.html"}, {"tag": "h4", "text": "a. [Production and Consumption]", "level": 4, "id": "ME29-15-5", "source_file": "MECW29-015.html", "chapter_number": 15, "filename": "MECW29-015.html"}, {"tag": "h4", "text": "b. [Production and Distribution]", "level": 4, "id": "ME29-15-6", "source_file": "MECW29-015.html", "chapter_number": 15, "filename": "MECW29-015.html"}, {"tag": "h4", "text": "c. Lastly, Exchange and Circulation", "level": 4, "id": "ME29-15-7", "source_file": "MECW29-015.html", "chapter_number": 15, "filename": "MECW29-015.html"}, {"tag": "h4", "text": "3. The method of political economy", "level": 4, "id": "ME29-15-8", "source_file": "MECW29-015.html", "chapter_number": 15, "filename": "MECW29-015.html"}, {"tag": "h3", "text": "4. Production", "level": 3, "id": "ME29-15-9", "source_file": "MECW29-015.html", "chapter_number": 15, "filename": "MECW29-015.html"}]}, {"file": "MECW29-016.html", "title": "Appendix: Index to the 7 Notebooks", "headings": [{"tag": "h1", "text": "Appendix: Index to the 7 Notebooks", "level": 0, "id": null, "source_file": "MECW29-016.html", "chapter_number": 16, "filename": "MECW29-016.html"}]}, {"file": "MECW29-017.html", "title": "Appendix: Original text of Second and beginning of Third chapter", "headings": [{"tag": "h1", "text": "Appendix: Original text of Second and beginning of Third chapter", "level": 0, "id": null, "source_file": "MECW29-017.html", "chapter_number": 17, "filename": "MECW29-017.html"}, {"tag": "h2", "text": "[Chapter Two, Money]", "level": 2, "id": "ME29-17-2", "source_file": "MECW29-017.html", "chapter_number": 17, "filename": "MECW29-017.html"}, {"tag": "h3", "text": "[2) Money As Means Of Payment]", "level": 3, "id": "ME29-17-3", "source_file": "MECW29-017.html", "chapter_number": 17, "filename": "MECW29-017.html"}, {"tag": "h3", "text": "3) Money As International Means of Payment and Purchase, As World Coin", "level": 3, "id": "ME29-17-4", "source_file": "MECW29-017.html", "chapter_number": 17, "filename": "MECW29-017.html"}, {"tag": "h3", "text": "4) The Precious Metals as Vehicles of the Money Relationship", "level": 3, "id": "ME29-17-5", "source_file": "MECW29-017.html", "chapter_number": 17, "filename": "MECW29-017.html"}, {"tag": "h3", "text": "5) The Manifestation of the Law of Appropriation in the Simple Circulation", "level": 3, "id": "ME29-17-6", "source_file": "MECW29-017.html", "chapter_number": 17, "filename": "MECW29-017.html"}, {"tag": "h3", "text": "6) Transition to Capital", "level": 3, "id": "ME29-17-7", "source_file": "MECW29-017.html", "chapter_number": 17, "filename": "MECW29-017.html"}, {"tag": "h2", "text": "Chapter Three. Capital", "level": 2, "id": "ME29-17-8", "source_file": "MECW29-017.html", "chapter_number": 17, "filename": "MECW29-017.html"}, {"tag": "h3", "text": "A) The Process of Production of Capital", "level": 3, "id": "ME29-17-9", "source_file": "MECW29-017.html", "chapter_number": 17, "filename": "MECW29-017.html"}, {"tag": "h5", "text": "1) The Transformation of Money into Capital", "level": 5, "id": "ME29-17-10", "source_file": "MECW29-017.html", "chapter_number": 17, "filename": "MECW29-017.html"}]}, {"file": "MECW29-018.html", "title": "Appendix: Additional Notes", "headings": [{"tag": "h1", "text": "Appendix: Additional Notes", "level": 0, "id": null, "source_file": "MECW29-018.html", "chapter_number": 18, "filename": "MECW29-018.html"}, {"tag": "h3", "text": "THE AESTHETIC PROPERTY OF GOLD", "level": 3, "id": "ME29-18-2", "source_file": "MECW29-018.html", "chapter_number": 18, "filename": "MECW29-018.html"}, {"tag": "h3", "text": "INVARIABLE VALUE OF MONEY", "level": 3, "id": "ME29-18-3", "source_file": "MECW29-018.html", "chapter_number": 18, "filename": "MECW29-018.html"}, {"tag": "h3", "text": "MONEY AS MONEY (WORLD COIN, ETC.)", "level": 3, "id": "ME29-18-4", "source_file": "MECW29-018.html", "chapter_number": 18, "filename": "MECW29-018.html"}, {"tag": "h3", "text": "FORM OF PROPERTY", "level": 3, "id": "ME29-18-5", "source_file": "MECW29-018.html", "chapter_number": 18, "filename": "MECW29-018.html"}]}, {"file": "MECW29-019.html", "title": "Appendix: Draft Plan of the Chapter on Capital", "headings": [{"tag": "h1", "text": "Appendix: Draft Plan of the Chapter on Capital", "level": 0, "id": null, "source_file": "MECW29-019.html", "chapter_number": 19, "filename": "MECW29-019.html"}]}, {"file": "MECW29-020.html", "title": "Appendix: References to My Own Notebooks", "headings": [{"tag": "h1", "text": "Appendix: References to My Own Notebooks", "level": 0, "id": null, "source_file": "MECW29-020.html", "chapter_number": 20, "filename": "MECW29-020.html"}]}]